            <title>[SPARK-40771] Estimated size in log message can overflow Int</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-40771</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The log message from&lt;br/&gt;
```&lt;br/&gt;
&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160;logInfo(s&quot;Started reading broadcast variable $id with $numBlocks pieces &quot; +&lt;br/&gt;
&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160;s&quot;(estimated total size $estimatedTotalSize)&quot;)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;```&lt;br/&gt;
multiples two ints to calculate `estimatedTotalSize` which will overflow when the broadcast exceeds 2Gib.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
